<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>SPORTMATCH — 서비스 점검 중</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Sans:ital,opsz,wght@0,9..40,300;0,9..40,400;0,9..40,500;0,9..40,600;0,9..40,700;1,9..40,400&family=DM+Mono:wght@400;500;700&family=Bebas+Neue&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
<div class="error-page">
  <div class="maintenance-bg"></div>
  <div class="error-bg-number">503</div>

  <div style="position:relative;z-index:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center">
    <div class="error-emoji">🔧</div>
    <div class="error-code">503 · Service Unavailable</div>
    <div class="error-title">잠깐, 점검 중이에요</div>
    <div class="eta-badge">
      <span style="width:7px;height:7px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--accent);display:inline-block;animation:pulse-dot 1s ease-in-out infinite"></span>
      예상 완료: <%= typeof eta !== 'undefined' ? eta : '약 30분 후' %>
    </div>
    <div class="error-desc">
      더 나은 SPORTMATCH를 위해 서버를 점검 중이에요.<br>
      잠시 후 더 빠르고 안정적으로 돌아올게요! 🏃
    </div>

    <div class="progress-section">
      <div class="progress-title">점검 진행 현황</div>
      <div class="progress-item">
        <div class="progress-icon p-done">✓</div>
        <div class="p-label">데이터베이스 마이그레이션</div>
        <div class="p-time">완료</div>
      </div>
      <div class="progress-item">
        <div class="progress-icon p-done">✓</div>
        <div class="p-label">캐시 서버 재시작</div>
        <div class="p-time">완료</div>
      </div>
      <div class="progress-item">
        <div class="progress-icon p-active">●</div>
        <div class="p-label">API 서버 배포</div>
        <div class="p-time">진행 중</div>
      </div>
      <div class="progress-item">
        <div class="progress-icon p-wait">○</div>
        <div class="p-label">서비스 검증 & 재오픈</div>
        <div class="p-time">대기</div>
      </div>
      <div class="overall-bar-wrap">
        <div class="overall-bar"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="overall-label">
        <span>점검 진행률</span>
        <span>약 65%</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
